org.eclipse.papyrus.RobotML

Interface Algorithm

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AlgorithmImpl

    public interface Algorithm
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Algorithm'. LibFileFormat can be elf, matlab, etc

    The following features are supported:

    • Base Operation
    • Is External
    • Ext Function Name
    • Lib Path
    • Lib File Format

    See Also:
    RobotMLPackage.getAlgorithm()
